       <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div id="crumbs" class="bradecrumbs">
         <a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog">Home</a>  
         <a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/category/technology-and-apps/">Technology and Apps</a>  
         <span class="current">9 Top JavaScript Frameworks For Mobile App Development</span>
        </div>
        <meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/technology-and-apps/top-javascript-frameworks-for-mobile-app-development/">
        <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="January 9, 2017">
        <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="July 24, 2017">
        <div class="single_blog_wrap">
         <div class="blogDetailTop">
          <h3>9 Top JavaScript Frameworks For Mobile App Development</h3> 
          <img src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/top-javascript-frameworks-comparision.jpg" class="featured-img" alt="9 Top JavaScript Frameworks For Mobile App Development" title="9 Top JavaScript Frameworks For Mobile App Development">
          <div class="at-above-post addthis_tool" data-url="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/technology-and-apps/top-javascript-frameworks-for-mobile-app-development/"></div>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Technically speaking, mobile apps in iOS, Android, and Windows Phone are coded using&nbsp; different programming languages.&nbsp; An iOS app uses Objective-C, an Android app is coded with Java, while a Windows Phone application uses .NET. However, with a decent knowledge in JavaScript, CSS and HTML, you can build awesome mobile apps. Therefore, in this blog&nbsp; we are going to discuss about top JavaScript frameworks for mobile apps </p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">You may also like: <a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/technology-and-apps/top-javascript-frameworks-list-comparison/" target="_blank">9 Top JavaScript Frameworks List In Todays Time(updated)</a></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">For web development, JavaScript has been a promising programming language and its not going anywhere in near future.&nbsp; However, does JavaScript has the same impact on mobile app development? lets find out.&nbsp;Here are 9 top JavaScript frameworks for mobile app development as per our research&nbsp; at <a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=home-5272&amp;utm_campaign=SMEs" target="_blank">ValueCoders</a>:</p>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: justify;">9 Top JavaScript Frameworks for Mobile</h3>
          <h4 style="margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: justify;"><a href="http://phonegap.com/">1) PhoneGap/Cordova</a></h4>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">PhoneGap (distribution of Apache Cordova) is a software development framework that helps you to reuse your existing web development skills to quickly make hybrid mobile applications built with HTML, CSS and JavaScript. Hence, this is not exactly a JavaScript framework, however, its important for you to know about PhoneGap before you get started.</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">PhoneGap works as a medium between your web application codes and mobile OS APIs. This diagram will help you understand better:</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works.png"><img style="margin-bottom: 25px;" class="crazy_lazy aligncenter size-full wp-image-5379" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works.png" alt="phonegap technology how it works" width="858" height="300" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works.png 858w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works-300x105.png 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works-768x269.png 768w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works-150x52.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 858px) 100vw, 858px">
            <noscript>
             <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5379" style="margin-bottom: 25px;" src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works.png" alt="phonegap technology how it works" width="858" height="300" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works.png 858w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works-300x105.png 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works-768x269.png 768w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/phonegap-technology-how-it-works-150x52.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 858px) 100vw, 858px">
            </noscript></a><em>Courtesy: phonegap.com</em></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">With the help of PhoneGap, you can use the same codes that you wrote in JavaScript, HTML &amp; CSS and generate APIs for mobile OS like Android and iOS.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;Apart from PhoneGap, there are a few more frameworks that can help convert your JavaScript files to mobile APIs. <a href="https://www.xamarin.com/" target="_blank">Xamarin</a>, <a href="https://ionicframework.com/" target="_blank">ionic,</a> <a href="https://coronalabs.com/" target="_blank">Corona</a> are some honorable mentions.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify;">Related: <a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/technology-and-apps/xamarin-ionic-choose-one/" target="_blank">Xamarin or ionic: which one to choose?</a></p>
          <hr>
          <h4 style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://www.appcelerator.com/mobile-app-development-products/" target="_blank">2) Titanium</a></h4>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Appcelerators Titanium is an open source application development platform that allows to create native apps (mobile and desktop) using web technologies, such as HTML, JavaScript,&nbsp; and CSS. The Titanium Mobile SDK is one of the most popular cross-platform mobile development solution in use today with over 916109 mobile developers and 460, 587, 474 devices are running Accelerator powered apps.</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Here is the architecture how Titanium works:</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture.jpg"><img style="margin-bottom: 25px;" class="crazy_lazy aligncenter wp-image-5395 size-full" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture.jpg" alt="titenium architechture- top javascript frameworks for mobile" width="800" height="305" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture.jpg 800w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture-300x114.jpg 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture-768x293.jpg 768w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture-150x57.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px">
            <noscript>
             <img class="aligncenter wp-image-5395 size-full" style="margin-bottom: 25px;" src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture.jpg" alt="titenium architechture- top javascript frameworks for mobile" width="800" height="305" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture.jpg 800w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture-300x114.jpg 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture-768x293.jpg 768w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/titenium-architechture-150x57.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px">
            </noscript></a></p>
          <hr>
          <h4 style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://mobileangularui.com/" target="_blank">3) jQuery Mobile</a></h4>
          <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1.png"><img style="margin-bottom: 25px;" class="crazy_lazy aligncenter size-full wp-image-5388" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1.png" alt="jquery mobile -logo (1)" width="100%" height="156" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1.png 550w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1-300x85.png 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1-150x43.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px">
            <noscript>
             <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5388" style="margin-bottom: 25px;" src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1.png" alt="jquery mobile -logo (1)" width="100%" height="156" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1.png 550w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1-300x85.png 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/jquery-mobile-logo-1-150x43.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px">
            </noscript></a></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">jQuery Mobile framework takes the write less, do more agenda to a next level. It is one of the top JavaScript frameworks for mobile to build an application or mobile friendly website.</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">jQuery Mobile supports a number of user interfaces that are compatible with modern platforms such as Android, iOS and to the earliest of platforms such as Opera Mini and Nokia Symbian. With the help of PhoneGap you can integrate your jQuery web app code to an interactive iOS or Android application.</p>
          <hr>
          <h4 style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://mobileangularui.com/" target="_blank">4) Sencha Touch</a></h4>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Sencha Touch(similar to <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ext_JS" target="_blank">Ext JS</a>)&nbsp; is said to be the only framework that offers optimal solutions to developers create fast and impressive mobile applications that work on&nbsp; Android, iOS,&nbsp; Kindle Fire, and more. It comes with lots of creative and useful components that work efficiently on all types of mobile applications. Here is a glimpse of the features.</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features.jpg"><img style="margin-bottom: 25px;" class="crazy_lazy aligncenter wp-image-5389 size-full" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features.jpg" alt="sencha-touch-features- top javascript frameworks for mobile" width="100%" height="448" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features.jpg 530w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features-300x254.jpg 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features-150x127.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px">
            <noscript>
             <img class="aligncenter wp-image-5389 size-full" style="margin-bottom: 25px;" src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features.jpg" alt="sencha-touch-features- top javascript frameworks for mobile" width="100%" height="448" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features.jpg 530w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features-300x254.jpg 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/sencha-touch-features-150x127.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px">
            </noscript></a></p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Here is a feature comparison of the above four frameworks</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Phonegap-vs-Titanium-vs-Jquery-Mobile-vs-Sencha-Touch.png"><img style="margin-bottom: 25px;" class="crazy_lazy aligncenter size-full wp-image-5491" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" data-src="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Phonegap-vs-Titanium-vs-Jquery-Mobile-vs-Sencha-Touch.png" alt="Phonegap vs Titanium vs Jquery Mobile vs Sencha Touch" width="848" height="345" srcset="https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Phonegap-vs-Titanium-vs-Jquery-Mobile-vs-Sencha-Touch.png 848w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Phonegap-vs-Titanium-vs-Jquery-Mobile-vs-Sencha-Touch-300x122.png 300w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Phonegap-vs-Titanium-vs-Jquery-Mobile-vs-Sencha-Touch-768x312.png 768w, https://www.valuecoders.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Phonegap-vs-Titanium-vs-Jquery-Mobile-vs-Sencha-Touch-150x61.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 848px) 100vw, 848px">
            <noscript>

          <h4 style="text-align: justify;"><a href="https://www.meteor.com/" target="_blank">6) Meteor</a></h4>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Meteor is yet another JavaScript framework that can help you develop in interactive mobile applications. Meteor not only allows your JavaScript code for mobile apps but also it gives you ongoing control over your app.&nbsp; With this feature you can update the JavaScript code without developers help and use the hot code push function to immediately deploy the changes to users on all mobile platforms.</p>
          <p style="text-align: justify;">Another specialty of Meteor(version: 1.0) is that it maintains a local copy of data by implementing its miniMongo database in phone internal memory.           <p style="text-align: justify;">One of the top JavaScript frameworks for mobile is Mobile Angular UI.&nbsp; If you are an Angular fan, then this framework is for you.               <div id="dsq-comment-message-593360" class="dsq-comment-message">
               <p>Thanks for the questions @Grauknot:disqus , its great that you made such an effort for the improvement of the blog. I am glad to answer all your question- Here are the answers</p>
               <p>1) At ValueCoders we have a large base of 450+ experienced developers who know JavaScript and mobile application development very well. Hence, we have a large source of information for our research. However, I apologize that I cant reveal the process of our research.</p>
               <p>2) Many people get confused with PhoneGap and Cordova. They think that they are two completely different identities. Only software professionals like you and me are aware of the real difference. However, thanks for giving your thoughts as a reader.</p>
               <p>3) This is not a ranking list. This is a list with 9 top JavaScript frameworks for mobile. I havent mentioned it anywhere that PhoneGap is No-1 or jQuery is no-2 or 3.<br> 4) If you have noticed that this list is for JavaScript admirers. I have mentioned Meteor as it is a pure JavaScript framework which Ionic &amp; Xamarin are not. For the same reason I have mentioned Angular UI &amp; Rachet.</p>
               <p>For details about Ionic and Xamarin please visit</p>
               <p>6) For the numbers regarding Titanium, I have rephrased according to your suggestion.</p>

              <div id="dsq-comment-message-593359" class="dsq-comment-message">
               <p>Some questions:<br> 1) You start out by saying [] as per our research at ValueCoders. How did you go about doing this research? What methods did you use to come up with the 9 top frameworks?</p>
               <p>2) PhoneGap is not known as Apache Cordova anymore, that was years ago. PhoneGap is a product by Adobe, Cordova is a product by Apache (which was donated to them by Adobe). You should also revise the rest of that section.</p>
               <p>3) Appcelerator Titanium does not power &gt;460 million apps (that would be ridiculous). However, &gt;460 million devices are running at least one Appcelerator-based app.</p>
               <p>4) How did jQuery Mobile and Sencha Touch land this high on the list? Again, how did you come up with these results?</p>
               <p>5) You honourably mention Ionic as part of the PhoneGap/Cordova section, but you have your own section for Meteor. Why? Meteor is also Cordova. Ionic shouldve had its own section, its vastly superior to several of the frameworks youve listed.</p>
               <p>6) Xamarin does not work in the same way as PhoneGap, and should seriously have its own section.</p>
               <p>7) Ratchets last commit was 9 months ago. For decision-making purposes, listing it in this blog post does not seem like a good idea.</p>
               <p>8) Seems odd that you list Mobile Angular UI instead of Ionic</p>
